### Advance

#### Set

~~~ .code-sample.php
Date::set($key = null, $fn = null ($output, $language));
~~~

Set custom date format:

~~~ .php
Date::set('my_format', function($output, $language) {
    return $output['year'] . '/' . $output['month'] . '/' . $output['day'];
});
~~~

Usage:

~~~ .php
$date = new Date('2016/04/21 16:00:00');

// [1]
echo $date->extract('my_format');

// [2]
echo $date->my_format;
~~~

#### Remove

~~~ .code-sample.php
Date::reset($key = null);
~~~

Remove custom date format:

~~~ .php
Date::reset('my_format');
~~~